snippet.title: Best VGM 1748 - Guardian's Crusade - Battle Theme
snippet.description:

Guardian's Crusade
Battle Theme
Mutsumi Ishimura, Akihi Motoyama, Yasuhiro Nakano, Fumio Tanabe & Luna Umegaki
